102
00:09:25,639 --> 00:09:26,639
I’m sorry for this.

103
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:32,120
But now I’m back.

104
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:36,159
Back to your side.

105
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,399
We will face and solve

106
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:40,759
all problems

107
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:41,799
