I found Shengnan

133
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:27,039
is changed since I’m back.

134
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,399
She’s

135
00:12:28,559 --> 00:12:30,000
keeping a distance with me deliberately,

136
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:32,080
