197
00:15:03,399 --> 00:15:04,120
No.

198
00:15:06,799 --> 00:15:09,279
I’m not joking with you.

199
00:15:09,279 --> 00:15:10,399
I’m not, either.

200
00:15:10,399 --> 00:15:11,559
I mean it.

201
00:15:11,879 --> 00:15:14,120
